(43) The perception of a self that has form is not existent; (44) it is not non-existent; (45) it is not both;
                                        and (46) it is not neither. (47) The perception of a self that has limit is not existent; (48) it is not non-existent;
                                        (49) it is not both; and (50) it is not neither.
